&lt;p&gt;
In this post I assert the Elmar was built in 1926--shows what the hell I know.  That&#039;s a date I pulled from a &lt;i&gt;Times&lt;/i&gt; article.  But lo and behold, here&#039;s the Elmar in 1921:
&lt;/p&gt;
